You can simply ask Alexa to control your MODENA LED Bulb. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1)Download our "MODENA Seamless" app in app market then register an account;
(2)Configure our devices in "MODENA Seamless" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3)Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure with "Alexa" app;
(4)Search "MODENA Seamless" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5)Enable "MODENA Seamless" skill, and you'll be navigated to MODENA Seamless login page;
(6)Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7)Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
